textAfterTable: In accordance with the Santa Cruz Academic Senate regulations, students qualify for the Dean's Honors List for a given term when they have completed a minimum of 15 units of which 10 are units for letter grade with a grade point average in the range required for University Honors at graduation for the current academic year (i.e. the top 15% of their academic group). Please visit the Honors frequently asked questions http://registrar.ucsc.edu/faqs/students/honors/index.html and contact us at ugrdhnrs@ucsc.edu if you have questions about Dean's Honors lists.
